Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因手段惡劣 警察立刻下達瞭解析IP地址的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,++++但是由於IP是經過VPN偽裝的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你能明白嗎 這些文字的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隔壁？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧 粗朵小姐 怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炸彈在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我隨便給了從樓下托兒所出來的一個小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.26,0:14:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.25,0:14:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你看 他們不煩人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.37,0:14:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得快點才行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.98,0:14:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經打電話給今天來托管的各位家長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要求他們檢查孩子的背包了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是因為已經是這個時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.18,0:14:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有幾位始終聯繫不上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.76,0:14:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察那邊也聯繫過了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.62,0:14:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對方表示會前往電話無法接通的家長那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是聽說不清楚能不能在預告時間之前趕到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.09,0:14:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有今天托管的兒童的名單嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:14:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會先前往距離最近的家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.80,0:14:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然也聯繫了大家 但是說實話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.95,0:15:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間實在是太少了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.41,0:15:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是已經沒有別的方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之轉告大家 保持手機和AQUARI Phone都能接通
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.99,0:15:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.26,0:15:21.76,post,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\frz-17\pos(720,192)}請大家告訴我和炸彈犯人\N在一起的孩子的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人的話 我看到他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.92,0:15:43.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傍晚的時候在阿佐谷公園和一個小孩子說話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.93,0:15:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是在廁所前面……。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.40,0:15:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了一個像是母親的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.21,0:15:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對小孩子說讓他等一等 然後進了廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了從阿佐谷公園前往商店街的母子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:16:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽穿了很華麗的黃色外套
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概就是那對母子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們在商店街的魚屋買了魚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.97,0:16:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做魚八屋的魚屋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.14,0:16:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魚八屋就是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家所說的應該是高井小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.65,0:16:20.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒記錯的話 今天有在我家買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高井…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了 高井達也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地址在…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.99,0:16:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請等一下 我們馬上就過去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 話雖這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻子小姐說她要自己去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店長這次怎麼這麼衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.03,0:16:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概想起了以前的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莊嚴社長 由文字建立起的聯繫絕對不是錯誤的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.31,0:16:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然稀少 但也有因此而得到救贖的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像那時的我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你附近有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是倉庫 離店很遠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有求救 但時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.37,0:17:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 現在救護車都出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最快也要30分鐘…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法…呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請盡量堅持
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.61,0:17:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也會盡量趕過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.31,0:17:36.86,post,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz-10\pos(495,294)}杉並第五櫻木大樓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.31,0:17:36.86,post,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz-10\pos(510,345)}被壓住了動不了 救命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附近的人趕緊去救人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是釣魚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去那裡要2小時
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才有個小地震來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.45,0:17:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是真的話可危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.82,0:17:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停車
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個孩子的包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.58,0:19:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了世界必須打倒莊嚴？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.57,0:19:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了和平？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了保護文字文化？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.41,0:19:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些全是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.30,0:19:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是不甘心而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人否定了…拯救了我的文字的聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:47.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就彷彿把曾經照亮我的那道光 那希望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都抹消掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.18,0:19:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不斷地戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.87,0:19:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想告訴他 他是錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.62,0:19:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是這樣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的…太差勁了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.76,0:20:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.38,0:20:14.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的聲音 能給與文字力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.43,0:20:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人君？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.62,0:20:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人君 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用管我了 只有你得救也好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店長…難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人 人君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.34,0:21:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店長…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人 不 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.93,0:21:16.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是也文字怪獸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.60,0:21:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能因為這點傷就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.77,0:21:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是文字怪獸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.23,0:21:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.76,0:21:38.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你陪我玩 阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.25,0:21:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的就是你自己的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.82,0:21:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有自我意識的你 已經是一個人類了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.52,0:22:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是人類…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.17,0:22:08.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 誰是阿姨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.92,0:22:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會生氣的 讓我好好對你生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.02,0:22:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人君…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.26,0:23:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 大家都不知道椰果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.30,0:23:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,NATA COCO？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.50,0:23:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.87,0:23:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和椰子是不同的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就叫代溝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.38,0:24:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 誰讓我是30的大媽了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.25,0:24:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泡沫和流行總是瞬間即逝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.83,0:24:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 第15話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.44,0:24:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚呼！青春年華
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.09,0:24:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要來看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
